Setup the index.handlebars to have the template that Handlebars can render onto.

Create a button in index.handlebars that will submit the user input into the database.

<h2>Add a Burger</h2>
<form class="create-update-form" action="/" method="POST">

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="bur">Name That Burger:</label>
    <input type="text" id="bur" name="name">
  </div>

  <div class="form-group">
    <label for="dev">Devour?</label><br>
    <input type="radio" name="devour" value="1" checked> Devoured!<br>
    <input type="radio" name="devoured" value="0"> Awake
  </div>

  <button type="submit">Add Burger</button>
</form>